nX: 其實我完成晒公司比我既工作，而且起呢段時間真係學到好多野，我相信自己有本事值呢個salary。<br />\n我﹕你都幾臉皮厚喎，連少少壓力都承受唔到，仲有咩資格話自己有本事值呢個salary<br />\nX: ......(啞左)<br />\n我﹕SORRY呀，我地公司覺得你唔值呢個價呀。無咩野既話，你可以走先架啦<br />\n<br />\n之後X小姐就頭dupdup，眼濕濕，然後垂頭喪氣咁走左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"樓豬開完post就潛水<br />\n真膠？假膠？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9331874488f4226e3efc0a9f5b51ec664aeac7b5","tid":598981,"uid":70135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"178212c01d81db3f5e9648fe48c7a2b2c3e386f5","tid":598981,"uid":19042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"78767d53c98e20d143a7b008b169a35ebc65e14b","tid":598981,"uid":11579,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"樓豬係咪唔抵得人地人工高過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:52:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾hr 值幾錢人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:46:55.000Z","msg":"大學生都得8000<br />\nHr 6000都唔值啦"},{"pid":"9dc87ff08d2d37dcb22e7f7a1c83654b431884d5","tid":598981,"uid":159530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"唔明點解裸辭同人工會掛勾, <br />\n辭左工先搵工有咩問題? <br />\n放個假減壓都要俾人質??<br />\n想搵個奴隸都醒少少, <br />\n咁樣interview, 請到返黎都唔會正常"},{"pid":"58374fc4fb86767e298bb5f6a589d4408e4f7b04","tid":598981,"uid":38910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:57:38.000Z","msg":"你都on99，出唔起錢就咪嘥人時間啦屌你"},{"pid":"19abbcb57defcf282a1026695262d3ee3c1592b8","tid":598981,"uid":146066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:57